  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nFor long deployment scripts, waiting txs for receipts and then broadcasting the next one can take a lot of time, it'd be nice to allow the user to broadcast them all (at the user's safety expense since one of them could revert).\r\nSince all txs are signed with a nonce, no reordering could happen that would make one prior to a previous one.\r\n\r\n`--slow` method seems to be selected by default, plz add `--fast` one üôè \r\n\r\nRelated to #5035 \n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
